snippet.title: Limerick: Cadence Mansion - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Next August 2023
snippet.description: Get a deep dive look at Limerick: Cadence Mansion from Jenito Studios to see gameplay, locations, weapons, upgrades, puzzles, and meet the creepy marionette antagonist named Limerick from this upcoming first-person action-horror adventure game. Limerick: Cadence Mansion will be available on PC in Fall 2023.
